    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cultural Context"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健康 is highly valued in Chinese culture as the foundation for all life achievements. Traditional\nChinese medicine emphasizes preventing illness and maintaining 健康 through balanced living. In\nmodern China, 健康 represents not just absence of disease but active vitality and well-being,\nencompassing physical fitness, mental balance, and social harmony."}],"type":"paragraph"}
